Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinkis are 15-centimeter-tall partners created to serve humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They are endowed with intelligence and emotion,\N and serve the one they call "Master".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can equip their Shinkis with whatever armor or weaponry they please,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and command them to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Some fight for honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,others to prove their strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and some simply strive for victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,These girls who do battle using the weapons given to them by their masters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are what we call "Busou Shinki"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP. No CCs for this one, sadly, but it sounds easy enough.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:26.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is endless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:33.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My eternal pledge is only for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:40.22,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I wonder if you're your usual self
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:45.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I'll sparkle with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Install dream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:58.59,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}The arms of the clock advance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:05.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and with them so does time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:12.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}When you are sad, I open my tiny arms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:18.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and embrace you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:27.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}My singing voice is tender
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:33.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}I can remember your shape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}and that wasn't brought about by a program
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Let us experience
