Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, wake up! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! You're in high school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be late for your entrance ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52}Now wake {\t(1000,0,\fs70)}up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Ann. {He says "An", but it's supposed to be short for "Arnval", that Shinki's model. As such, Arn.}{Ignore that, I've since changed my views.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning. I'm up now, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still waiting on a few boxes of luggage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've got nothing but furniture for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you, Dad? Isn't it midnight over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't catch a cold or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be late if I don't head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably under the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you forgot your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there should be some luggage coming in later,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so I need you to sign for it, Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm of—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Luggage here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you'll be late if you don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the unpacking while you're gone, so leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,where shall I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}here's{\i0} a start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines! {Model name: Altines}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit hogging the spotlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only one who got to ride with Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had only thrown scissors back there, {\i1}I{\i0} would've been on that train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get full of yourself just because you've been with Master the longest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you {\i1}say{\i0} that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, I've lived with Master in this house ever since he was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but your words cut like a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda cheap soap opera did you learn {\i1}that{\i0} from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for sleeping in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He already left for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we're in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's childhood home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's childhood room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, she ain't listenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And this must be Master's hometown!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk about Master's hometown later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, how about we start unpacking Master's luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And stop acting. We've known each other for years now. {* Lit. appears to be: Stop that careless appeal that we've known about since childhood. I dunno.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh no! {Overlaps with previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'll get ready right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that wearing Maid Costume Armor is perfect for tidying up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some spare time on the plane ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some for you two as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening. And won't it be hard to move in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels... a little tight on my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I made this one for Ines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that on purpose, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, neither of you are dressing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,5,,Let's just get everything unpacked first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.81,Default,,0,0,5,,We'll leave the Maid Costume Armor for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,5,,All right, let's get it started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,5,,"Important"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,5,,What's in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,5,,Things that are important to Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.12,Default,,0,0,5,,Important to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important, so... a charm, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something he should be wearing, not packing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Money is something everyone in the world finds important, not just Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, it's probably got something to do with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they say the one thing most important to young boys
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are the books they hide under their beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you hear these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit dusty in here, so let's open a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's so warm outside! It feels wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Master'll be proud that we cleaned this place up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They say there's nothing better than a spotless home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I wonder what you're doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how nostalgic! {Ann seems like the type to use "nostalgic".}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Master engraved a mark on that wall every time he grew taller!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to cheat a bit and stand on his tiptoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but even that was just so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're about done unpacking. {Sexualized loli robot ass is da best}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's important luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell put a {\i1}knife{\i0} there, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! We have to open it to make sure the contents are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}told{\i0} you, maid costumes aren't cut out for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Robotics... Monthly"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you meant by important books?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it's meant to be hidden under a bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this important too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these items really so important to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is this a love letter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! You can't just look at Master's letters without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But this letter might be addressed to one of us! {You will never give a love letter to your 6" loli robot. ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,F-For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We should open it to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get permission first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, you wanna know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—huh? I never said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if he wrote it for a human girl, and not us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That would hurt a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's important letter!{this letter flies better than any paper plane I ever folded}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search right, so you two search left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Such killing intent... {translated poorly for added comic effect}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what i—bwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have fallen around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you three from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you pull a surprise attack on {\i1}me{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the second place victor of last year's Busou Shinki tournament?! {Not sure if "second place" and "victor" cancel each other out}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got... some... nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet! Time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of common courtesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you regret this slight by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Field, expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A Battle Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we apologize, but we're in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late for excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away is against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve challenging us to a Street Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that from cowards who rely on surprise attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How dare you shoot at Master's letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Seems like you're ready to fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle Field, forcibly retracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ines, Lene, we should hurry home! {Lene's model: Altlene}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My master's coming home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got held pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.39,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You two got here safe and sound? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you were lonely without me, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you a dandelion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You three really cleaned this place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're sorry. Your important letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was a little burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Important letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we didn't read what was inside, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... what was this, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A visualizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a modified Shinki House I made. {*Not sure what 改造して means here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ann, remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the room Master made for me the first day I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, {\i1}I'm{\i0} not jealous or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, the room belongs to the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome again, Ann, Ines, Lene.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll get the sewing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we all wear that Maid Costume Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't this room a bit too cutesy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather do some remodeling and make it look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Starting today, we'll be helping you live on your own in Japan, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I don't remember packing a box like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone give you that as a moving gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED. Also not CC'd}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:26.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I stand here reflected in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:31.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and make something of a foolish face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:39.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Being more gentle than the wind and invincible like the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:44.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:51.93,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Here in the forest I am lost in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}I want to try finding a four-leaf clover
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:04.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}The sun is guiding me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.79,0:23:10.51,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}towards the miracles of two stars together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:13.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Even if we are hurt on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:17.68,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and ten years pass
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:24.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}this future where I can be with you is what I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.17,0:23:25.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}We will walk on ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:30.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}and not miss the sun's sign
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the move's over and done with, I can't wait to see what our new life with Master will be like!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, but aren't you curious about the important books that Master keeps under his bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm more worried about that Strarf-model Shinki. Who the heck is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, a heavily-armed Strarf joins us! {*I'm not sure what 武闘派 means here}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An action-packed battle is about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.95,0:24:00.66,Default,,0,0,5,,We're going to make delicious food for Master!
